### STATIC EXCHANGE EVALUATION
```
function SEE(square, attacker, target):
    gain[0] = value[target]
    attacker = next_attacker(square)
    depth = 1
    
    while attacker exists:
        gain[depth] = value[attacker] - gain[depth-1]
        if gain[depth] < 0 and depth % 2 = 0:
            break
        if gain[depth] > 0 and depth % 2 = 1:
            break
        attacker = next_attacker(square)
        depth = depth + 1
    
    while depth > 1:
        depth = depth - 1
        if depth % 2 = 1:
            gain[depth-1] = -max(-gain[depth-1], gain[depth])
        else:
            gain[depth-1] = max(gain[depth-1], -gain[depth])
    
    return gain[0]
```

