### CUE BALL PATH GEOMETRY

#### Aiming Point for Straight Shot
```
Target ball at (x_t, y_t)
Pocket at (x_p, y_p)
Aim point = (x_t, y_t) - 2r × (x_t - x_p, y_t - y_p) / d_tp
where d_tp = √((x_t - x_p)² + (y_t - y_p)²)
```

#### Ghost Ball Method
```
Ghost ball position = (x_t, y_t) - 2r × (cos θ, sin θ)
where θ = arctan2(y_t - y_p, x_t - x_p)
