## PHYSICS OF BILLIARD SHOTS

### CUE BALL DYNAMICS

#### Initial Velocity from Cue Stroke
```
v₀ = √(2E/m) where E = ½mv² from cue energy
```

#### Cue Ball Spin
```
Top spin (follow): ω > 0
Back spin (draw): ω < 0
