## COMPUTATIONAL ALGORITHMS

### CONVERSION ALGORITHMS

#### Gregorian to Mayan Long Count
```
function gregorian_to_mayan(year, month, day):
    JDN = gregorian_to_jdn(year, month, day)
    days = JDN - 584285
    B = floor(days / 144000)
    days = days mod 144000
    K = floor(days / 7200)
    days = days mod 7200
    T = floor(days / 360)
    days = days mod 360
    U = floor(days / 20)
    Kin = days mod 20
    return (B, K, T, U, Kin)
```

#### Long Count to Calendar Round
```
function long_count_to_calendar_round(B, K, T, U, Kin):
    days = B×144000 + K×7200 + T×360 + U×20 + Kin
    Haab_day = days mod 365
    H_month = floor(Haab_day / 20)
    H_day = Haab_day mod 20
    
    Tzolk_day = days mod 260
    T_number = (Tzolk_day mod 13) + 1
    T_name_index = Tzolk_day mod 20
    
    return (H_month, H_day, T_number, T_name_index)
```

